                            <h3>Language(s)</h3>
                            <p class="tour-extra"><a target="instructionsviewer" rel="nofollow" onclick="var w=window.open('/TBL/WebObjects/ToursByLocals.woa/1/wa/textPopup?c=34&amp;wosid=DnEWhJv4xDWKtItObhIqkM','instructionsviewer','toolbar=no,location=no,status=no,menubar=no,resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=700,height=600'); w.focus(); return false" href="/TBL/WebObjects/ToursByLocals.woa/1/wa/textPopup?c=34&amp;wosid=DnEWhJv4xDWKtItObhIqkM">explanation</a></p>
